Package com.amonson.prop_store

Class PropStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amonson.prop_store.PropStore
  • public abstract class PropStore
extends java.lang.Object
    Class representing a Store of properies (maps/lists nested or flat). Any stream, reader/writer, or files can be used.
